title: Kpop Demon Hunters Rumi Youtooz Vinyl Figure
body_html:
Watch out, demons, Rumi's here to seal you away with her Youtooz debut!

Standing at 4.7 inches tall with her left hand resting on the golden hilt of a blue and purple sword that has its curved tip resting on the ground, a pink-lipped smile crosses her calm face as a thick braid of purple hair falls down her back. With pale purple patterns working their way across her body and face, she wears a gold trimmed white tank top and shorts, along with knee high laced boots.

The exterior of her packaging sees a glowing sword amongst hazy pink and blue hues, while the interior is filled with a deep blue that's covered in small white dots. The protective sleeve is then a soft blue to purple gradient with thin lines wrapping over its surface, as her figure can be seen through the large, clear window at the packaging's front. This collectible ships in a matte, embossed, protective outer sleeve and a custom-sized plastic protector for maximum protection during shipping.

  • Preorder figure is non-refundable
  • Size: Height: 4.7"
